ShareUp Story

ShareUp started in Qatar(Middle East) with the aim of being the most private and secure social media in the world. Our founder Mr. Firat Yagmur came up with a wonderful and unique idea of sharing platform where people can connect from heart to heart. More than that, it is secure and protects your privacy with the most trending technology we use. We provide you most private and secure social media platform. Your data is our concern. You Share, we share and everyone share. Lets share without fear. You are our concern, not our target.
